{
  "title": "Static有什么用途",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Static</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有什么用途</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关键字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的作用是什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">限制变量的作用域</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">设置变量的存储域</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">堆，主动分配内存也是堆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">定义静态局部变量，作用域从函数开始到结束</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在模块内的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">函数只可被这一模块内的其它函数调用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这个函数的使用范围被限制在声明它的模块内；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在类中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">成员变量属于整个类所拥有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对类的所有对象只有一份拷贝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p></div><span title=\"neteasefooter\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px;\"><span id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div id=\"netease_mail_footer\"><div style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 10px 5px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px;\"></div></div></span></span>"
    }
  ]
}